<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:12:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>ASML预计美国、荷兰出口规则将使中国销售额下降10-15%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-expects-us-dutch-export-rules-hit-china-sales-by-10-15-2024-01-24/</link><description>荷兰计算机芯片设备制造商 ASML 周三表示，预计美国和荷兰的新出口限制将使其今年对中国的潜在销售额减少约 10-15%，此前这些销售额在 2023 年创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-expects-us-dutch-export-rules-hit-china-sales-by-10-15-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>查看中国央行采取行动支持市场和经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-central-bank-acts-support-markets-economy-2024-01-24/</link><description>周三，中国央行行长潘功胜表示，中国央行将从 2 月 5 日起削减银行必须持有的现金准备金数额，这是政策制定者加大力度支撑脆弱的经济复苏之际今年的首次削减。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-central-bank-acts-support-markets-economy-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺提供援助情绪，富时 100 指数上涨，易捷航空攀升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-gains-china-pledges-aid-sentiment-easyjet-climbs-2024-01-24/</link><description>英国蓝筹股指数周三上涨，受到英国央行采取措施支持经济的中国股市的提振，而易捷航空 (Easyjet) 的股价在该航空公司预测亏损较小后上涨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:42:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-gains-china-pledges-aid-sentiment-easyjet-climbs-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国将从下月起降低银行存款准备金率以支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-cut-banks-reserve-ratio-next-month-bolster-economic-recovery-2024-01-24/</link><description>周三，中国央行行长潘功胜表示，中国央行将从 2 月 5 日起削减银行必须持有的现金准备金数额，这是政策制定者加大力度支撑脆弱的经济复苏之际今年的首次削减。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-cut-banks-reserve-ratio-next-month-bolster-economic-recovery-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>诺基亚与中国 Oppo 通过交叉许可协议解决纠纷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-chinas-oppo-resolve-disputes-through-cross-license-deal-2024-01-24/</link><description>芬兰电信设备制造商诺基亚周三表示，已与中国设备制造商 Oppo 签署了 5G 专利交叉许可协议，解决了两家公司之间的专利诉讼。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-chinas-oppo-resolve-disputes-through-cross-license-deal-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>低排放电力的增长预计将满足需求 - IEA</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/growth-low-emissions-power-expected-cover-demand-iea-2024-01-24/</link><description>国际能源署（IEA）表示，风能、太阳能和核能等低排放能源产生的电力将足以满足未来三年全球需求的增长，并补充说电力部门的排放量正在下降。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/growth-low-emissions-power-expected-cover-demand-iea-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>ASML 第四季度订单激增，但 2024 年前景保持不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-fourth-quarter-earnings-beat-expectations-keeps-outlook-unchanged-2024-01-24/</link><description>芯片制造设备制造商阿斯麦控股周三公布的第四季度收益超出预期，且季度订单创历史新高，但由于面临对中国出口的新限制，该公司对 2024 年的前景保持谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 06:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-fourth-quarter-earnings-beat-expectations-keeps-outlook-unchanged-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>面对中国电动汽车的激烈竞争，日本电产下调盈利预测18%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/japans-nidec-nearly-doubles-operating-profit-third-quarter-2024-01-24/</link><description>日本电机制造商日本电产株式会社周三将全年营业利润预期下调近五分之一，警告中国电动汽车市场的需求不确定性和价格竞争加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 06:28:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/japans-nidec-nearly-doubles-operating-profit-third-quarter-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾当选总统表示希望加入美国主导的贸易框架</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-elect-signals-desire-join-us-led-trade-framework-2024-01-24/</link><description>台湾当选总统赖清德周三表示，考虑到台湾在全球经济中的关键作用，他希望台北加入美国主导的印太经济框架。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 06:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-elect-signals-desire-join-us-led-trade-framework-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>逆向投资者察觉机遇，中国卖空者撤退</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-short-sellers-retreat-contrarians-sense-an-opportunity-2024-01-24/</link><description>全球投资者对今年中国经济的预期并不高，但一些人表示，本已便宜的股市暴跌值得押注于最终反弹，或许还需要采取新的市场投资方式。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-short-sellers-retreat-contrarians-sense-an-opportunity-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国股市或芭比娃娃运气不佳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-01-24/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:36:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>蒙古官员称天然气卡车爆炸造成六名消防员死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/three-firefighters-among-six-killed-gas-truck-explosion-mongolia-officials-2024-01-24/</link><description>据蒙古紧急情况官员称，周三，一辆载有60吨液化天然气的卡车在蒙古首都乌兰巴托发生爆炸，造成至少六人死亡，其中包括三名消防员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/three-firefighters-among-six-killed-gas-truck-explosion-mongolia-officials-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国要求中国敦促伊朗遏制胡塞武装袭击红海 - FT</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-china-help-curb-red-sea-attacks-by-iran-backed-houthis-ft-2024-01-24/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周三援引美国官员的话报道称，美国已要求中国敦促德黑兰遏制与伊朗结盟的胡塞武装在红海袭击商船，但北京几乎没有提供帮助的迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:16:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-china-help-curb-red-sea-attacks-by-iran-backed-houthis-ft-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟制定经济安全计划 关注中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-draws-up-economic-security-plans-with-mind-china-2024-01-24/</link><description>欧盟委员会将于周三制定计划，通过对外国投资进行更严格的审查以及对向中国等竞争对手的出口和技术外流进行更协调的控制来加强欧盟的经济安全。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:04:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-draws-up-economic-security-plans-with-mind-china-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特斯拉计划于 2025 年中期生产新款电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-plans-build-new-electric-vehicles-mid-2025-sources-2024-01-24/</link><description>据四位知情人士透露，特斯拉已告知供应商，希望在 2025 年中期开始生产一款代号为“Redwood”的新型大众市场电动汽车，其中两人将该车型描述为紧凑型跨界车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-plans-build-new-electric-vehicles-mid-2025-sources-2024-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>